name: GRND by Fever of Unknown Origin (FUO)

metadata.name: GRND #0001
metadata.description: GRND by Fever of Unknown Origin (FUO). A fan economy based collectibles project dedicated by Social-Fi&Game-Fi project FUO. The original character illustrations of this project were inspired by the world famous J-pop group GARNiDELiA, and were designed by a globally popular Gen Z illustrator YULIA. The whole collection size is 1,000 with unique Japanese style elements, and shows the creative world of GARNiDELiA.
